name: rc-v1.7.0
body:
- Data points can now have notes that show up under any graph they are a part of

- Tracked data can now have optional more detailed descriptions

- Swapped order of default tracking input types 

- Two more data visualisation colors to use

- Various minor bug fixes

- Due to compatibility issues the minimum API level has been raised to 21 (Android version 5.0 Lollipop)

name: v1.6.1
body: Fix for navigation menu showing wrong icon between back and burger icon

name: rc-v1.6.0
body:
- Added basic tracking widget for easy tracking from the home screen

- Added line point label options to line graphs to make reading certain graphs easier

- Added hourly plot totals option to line graph

- Removed timestamp only data type but added a more general default value option to make tracking certain things faster and easier

- You can now select more than one of the multiple choice answers when creating an "Average time between" or "Time since last" statistic

- Added a backup and restore page to allow quick backing up of all app data including track groups, graph groups and reminders
